{lang-eng}Bhayapadakumu neevu yuddamu
Yehovaade nishchayamuga jayamu
Neede bhaya padakumu{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Garjinchu simhamu vale shatruvu neepaini
Bada joochu chunde nadivale neepai paara
Vachchunu yuddamu Yehovade bhayapadaku{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Paalu thenelu pravahinchedu kaananu mee
Yeduta nunde shatruvu ninnu jampa jooche
Yuddamu Yehovaade bhayapadaku{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Neeku virodhamuga roopinchu ye aayudhamu
Vardhilladu prati naaluka theerpuku lonagunu
Yuddamu Yehovaade bhaya padaku{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Neevu poraadedu paniledu nammakamunchi
Viswaasamutho rakshananu thilakinchumu
Jayamu prabhuvude bhayapadaku{/lang-eng}
